Conenct the rpi and the laptop to the same network

Connect the joystick to the laptop.

ros2 run joy joy_node //ros2 topic echo /joy to check the values


Converting joy to twist messages.

ros2 launch teleop_twist_joy teleop-launch.py joy_config:='xbox'  // ros2 topic echo /cmd_vel to check

NOTE: Make sure you are pressing the RB on the controller for the values to be registered and updated.


Run the packages to get the desired outputs.

